  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3048885">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3048885/" class="title-link">《水经注校证》的错误举例</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3048885"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/christwood/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1504424-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/christwood/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">伯虓甫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-08"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-08 04:37:44</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3048885_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  陈桥驿先生的新作《水经注校证》一书，错误很多。兹举一例：  卷二，校正（一）：《注疏》本作“河水二”。《疏》：“赵云：凡经文次篇之首，有某水二字，皆后人所加，盖汉人作《经》，自为一篇，岂能逆料。”《注疏》本又云：“郦氏为之《注》，而先于每卷交割之处，增二字以...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3048885/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">19有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3048885_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3048885_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










